select count(IDNR) from sm_geraeteview ge WITH(NOLOCK) inner join SM_Kontakt_Kunde kd WITH(NOLOCK) on (ge.Ebene1=kd.Ebene1 and ge.Ebene2=kd.Ebene2 and ge.Ebene3=kd.Ebene3 and ge.Ebene4=kd.Ebene4 and ge.BETREIBER=kd.KDNR and kd.EMailAdresse=':6' and kd.Projekt=:7 and kd.Aktiv=1)
where ge.Ebene1=:1 and ge.Ebene2=:2 and ge.Ebene3=:3 and ge.Ebene4=:4 and Hersteller=':5'

select count(IDNR) from sm_geraeteview ge WITH(NOLOCK) inner join SM_Kontakt_Kunde kd WITH(NOLOCK) on (ge.Ebene1=kd.Ebene1 and ge.Ebene2=kd.Ebene2 and ge.Ebene3=kd.Ebene3 and ge.Ebene4=kd.Ebene4 and ge.BETREIBER=kd.KDNR and kd.EMailAdresse=':6' and kd.Projekt=:7 and kd.aktiv=1)
where ge.Ebene1=:1 and ge.Ebene2=:2 and ge.Ebene3=:3 and ge.Ebene4=:4 and Modell=':5'

Select g.Ebene1,g.Ebene2,g.Ebene3,g.Ebene4,g.IDNR,g.ModellBezeichnung, iz.RO_Kostenstelle From GERAETE g WITH(NOLOCK) inner join SM_Kontakt_Kunde kd WITH(NOLOCK) on (kd.Ebene1=g.Ebene1 and kd.Ebene2=g.Ebene2 and kd.Ebene3=g.Ebene3 and kd.Ebene4=g.Ebene4 and kd.KDNR=g.BETREIBER and kd.EMailAdresse=':5' and kd.Projekt=:6) inner join IDNR_ZUSATZ iz WITH(NOLOCK) on (iz.Ebene1=g.Ebene1 and iz.Ebene2=g.Ebene2 and iz.Ebene3=g.Ebene3 and iz.Ebene4=g.Ebene4 and iz.IDNR=g.IDNR) Where g.Ebene1=:1 and g.Ebene2=:2 and g.Ebene3=:3 and g.Ebene4=:4 order by RO_Kostenstelle

select distinct p.Auftrags_Datum, gz.SucFleetHostname, p.AUFTNR, g.Serien_Nr, k.Matchcode, ABS(isnull(p.Bestellmenge,0))-abs(isnull(p.Liefermenge,0)) as Offen, p.IDNR, ak.BestellNrr, ak.Datum, ak.Erstell_Uhrzeit, v.ShipcloudStatus, v.ShipcloudStatusDatum, v.ShipcloudStatusZeit, isnull(sh.StatusSmartmanager,10) as StatusSmartmanager, isnull(ak.Lieferanschrift_1,'') as Name1, isnull(ak.Lieferanschrift_2,'') as Name2, isnull(ak.Lieferanschrift_3,'') as Name3, ak.Lieferstraee, ak.Liefer_Plz, ak.Liefer_Ort from positionen p WITH(NOLOCK) inner join Ebene4 e WITH(NOLOCK) on e.Ebene1=p.Ebene1 and e.Ebene2=p.Ebene2 and e.Ebene3=p.Ebene3 and e.Ebene4=p.Ebene4 inner join geraete g WITH(NOLOCK) on (p.Ebene1=g.Ebene1 and p.Ebene2=g.Ebene2 and p.Ebene3=g.Ebene3 and p.Ebene4=g.Ebene4 and p.IDNR = g.IDNR) inner join GERAETE_ZUSATZ gz WITH(NOLOCK) on (p.Ebene1=gz.Ebene1 and p.Ebene2=gz.Ebene2 and p.Ebene3=gz.Ebene3 and p.Ebene4=gz.Ebene4 and p.IDNR = gz.IDNR) inner join kunden k WITH(NOLOCK) on (k.Ebene1=CASE WHEN p.zentral_KDNR = 1 THEN e.ZentralEbene1 ELSE p.Ebene1 END and k.Ebene2=CASE WHEN p.zentral_KDNR = 1 THEN e.ZentralEbene2 ELSE p.Ebene2 END and k.Ebene3=CASE WHEN p.zentral_KDNR = 1 THEN e.ZentralEbene3 ELSE p.Ebene3 END and k.Ebene4=CASE WHEN p.zentral_KDNR = 1 THEN e.ZentralEbene4 ELSE p.Ebene4 END and p.KDNR = k.KDNR) inner join SM_Kontakt_Kunde pk WITH(NOLOCK) on (pk.Ebene1=p.Ebene1 and pk.Ebene2=p.Ebene2 and pk.Ebene3=p.Ebene3 and pk.Ebene4=p.Ebene4 and pk.KDNR=p.KDNR and pk.Projekt=:7 and pk.aktiv=1) inner join AUFTRAGKOPF ak WITH(NOLOCK) on (ak.Ebene1=p.Ebene1 and ak.Ebene2=p.Ebene2 and ak.Ebene3=p.Ebene3 and ak.Ebene4=p.Ebene4 and ak.AuftragsNr =p.AUFTNR) left outer join versand_etik_kopf v WITH(NOLOCK) on (v.Ebene1=p.Ebene1 and v.Ebene2=p.Ebene2 and v.Ebene3=p.Ebene3 and v.Ebene4=p.Ebene4 and v.VorgangNr = ak.VersandVorgangsNr) left outer join SHIPCLOUD_STATUS_SM sh WITH(NOLOCK) on (sh.Ebene1=p.Ebene1 and sh.Ebene2=p.Ebene2 and sh.Ebene3=p.Ebene3 and sh.Ebene4=p.Ebene4 and sh.StatusShipcloud=v.ShipcloudStatus) where p.Ebene1=:1 and p.Ebene2=:2 and p.Ebene3=:3 and p.Ebene4=:4 and p.Auftrags_Datum>':5' and Auft0Rep1W2AL3AL3=0 and pk.EMailAdresse=':6' and (ak.Geschaeftsfall = (select st.defaultGFVBMoVertrag from SCFleet_Steuerfile st WITH(NOLOCK) where st.Ebene1=:1 and st.Ebene2=:2 and st.Ebene3=:3 and st.Ebene4=:4) or ak.Geschaeftsfall = (select st.defaultGFVBMVertrag from SCFleet_Steuerfile st WITH(NOLOCK) where st.Ebene1=:1 and st.Ebene2=:2 and st.Ebene3=:3 and st.Ebene4=:4) ) order by AUFTNR
delete from ro_dashboardskontakt where Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4 and Projekt=:5 and EMailadresse=':6'
